# Test coverage

- **Target:** total coverage for the `dynamicapiclient` package must stay **≥ 90%** (pytest-cov with branch coverage enabled, same settings as `pyproject.toml`).
- **Scope:** all modules under `src/dynamicapiclient/` — when adding or changing code, add or extend tests so new branches and lines remain covered. Do not lower `--cov-fail-under` to “make CI green” without restoring coverage.
- **Check locally:** `pytest -q --cov=dynamicapiclient --cov-fail-under=90` (or `pre-commit run --all-files` after hooks are installed).
